{% comment %}
  Free Gift Engine — app EMBED. This is the ENGINE: it loads the storefront controller site-wide
  (every page, so it reacts to the cart drawer opening from anywhere), renders a hidden config element
  the controller reads, and provides the chooser mount the perception UI renders into.

  Enable it in the theme editor under: Theme settings (gear) -> App embeds -> "Free Gift Engine".

  Phase 5b-2a: the OR/variant chooser + decline checkbox render into [data-fge-chooser] from the
  read-only campaign config (GET /apps/free-gift/config). The old `default_choices` setting (a 5b-1
  seam that needed manual tier-id JSON and broke on every re-seed) is RETIRED — choices now come from
  the shopper's selection. The tier progress graph + pending hint + placement/mobile polish are 5b-2b.
{% endcomment %}

<div
  data-fge-app-block
  data-proxy-path="/apps/free-gift/validate"
  data-presentment-currency="{{ cart.currency.iso_code }}"
  data-country="{{ localization.country.iso_code }}"
  hidden
></div>

{% comment %} Chooser mount (visible). 5b-2b moves/styles this into the cart drawer. {% endcomment %}
<div data-fge-chooser class="fge-chooser-mount"></div>

<script src="{{ 'free-gift.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Free Gift Engine",
  "target": "body",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
